      hinglish: ['Aur tum maal se bohat zyada <b>mohabbat rakhte</b> ho. - watu<b>ḥibbū</b>na l-māla <b>ḥubban</b> jamman', 'Beshak Allah <b>daane</b> aur guthli ko phaadne wala hai. - inna llāha fāliqu l-<b>ḥabbi</b> wan-nawā']
