      hinglish: ['Woh aur unki biwiyan saayon mein takhton par takiya lagaye <b>khush honge</b>. - hum wa-azwājuhum fī ẓilālin ʿalā l-arā’iki muttaki’ūna yu<b>ḥbarū</b>na', '...aur beshak bohat se <b>ulama</b> aur darvesh logon ka maal na-haq khaate hain... - ...wa-inna kathīran mina l-a<b>ḥbāri</b> war-ruhbāni laya’kulūna amwāla n-nāsi bil-bāṭili']
